text: "Who Owns My Heart" is a 2010 song by Miley Cyrus and is the second and final single from her third studio album Can't Be Tamed. It went to the top 40 in Austria, Germany, Hungary, Romania and Russia and was the final single released from Hollywood Records. ==References== Category:2010 songs Category:Miley Cyrus songs Category:Electropop songs
title: Who Owns My Heart
